[Better safe than sorry. The Fraser Valley is much used by migratory
birds so this is a wise warning to the poultry farmers in British
Columbia. To find the Fraser Valley go to
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fraser_Valley.

The 2004 incident is well covered in the ProMED-mail postings of the
time; see links posts listed below. - Mod MHJ]

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of British Columbia can be
seen at http://healthmap.org/r/1p4x. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]
